to suggestions.

02:51.500 --> 02:53.700
Really? Good! Here.

02:54.900 --> 02:56.300
The Buena Burbank Apartments.

02:56.300 --> 02:58.900
They have really cute
one bedrooms.

02:59.300 --> 03:00.300
See, I can't afford this.

03:00.300 --> 03:02.100
We could together. We're ready

03:02.100 --> 03:03.300
