03:03.300 --> 03:04.700
Wow. We...

03:04.900 --> 03:06.000
That's, um...

03:06.700 --> 03:08.300
That's a very big
step, you know, and

03:08.300 --> 03:10.200
I think that it's not something
that you should rush into.

03:10.200 --> 03:11.900
I think that it's something
you should discuss.

03:11.900 --> 03:13.200
I mean, look at this
place, all right?

03:13.200 --> 03:16.400
72-inch plasma,
super comfy couches,

03:16.400 --> 03:17.500
