we can drink.

03:17.500 --> 03:18.500
I mean, come on, baby.

03:18.500 --> 03:20.500
We are living the dream.

03:20.500 --> 03:22.200
Whose dream, Morgan?

03:24.700 --> 03:25.600
Everyone's.

03:27.700 --> 03:29.900
Hey, Chuck, you ever wonder

03:29.900 --> 03:31.700
